task.summary:
Complete Phase 2 + UI polish: inventory CRUD, form validation, NrSelect
Phase 2 backend: - Inventory create/edit/delete/bulk_assign — all ownership-guarded - edit rebuilds var_maps from attr_* fields; vrfs split to list - bulk_assign accepts JSON {profile_id, device_ids}
Form validation (site-wide): - novalidate + .field-error + shake on all forms (login, register, inventory, security profiles) - nr-submitted: empty required fields show error on submit attempt - nr-touched: selects silent on load, only complain on submit - Validation state cleared on modal close — no stale errors on reopen - base.html gets same CSS/JS so login page is covered
NrSelect widget: - CSS moved to operator_base.html (available site-wide) - Platform selector in inventory add/edit modals replaced with NrSelect showing vendor logos - Test connection device dropdown replaced with NrSelect (logo + IP)
Bug fixes: - Double flash on inventory page removed - OTP box shake was silently broken (double get_flashed_messages drained queue) — fixed with {% set flash_messages %}
Visual polish: - Variable attributes expand toggle matches nr-label (color #777, weight 500) - Tooltip row keys match nr-label

